# Developer & Designer Graduation Mantra Generator
A beautiful web application that generates personalized professional
mantras for developers and designers beginning their careers.

## ğŸŒŸ Features

-   Personalized Mantras based on user input
-   Beautiful UI with modern styling and animations
-   Free Forever --- no API keys required
-   Reliable + offline-safe template fallback system
-   Responsive across mobile and desktop

## ğŸš€ Quick Start

### Prerequisites

-   Node.js (version 14+)
-   A modern web browser

